text: Jordan Fisher and Lindsay Arnold, winners of “ Dancing With the Stars ” Season 25. ( ABC / Adam Rose ) In a not - surprising turn of events, actor Jordan Fisher won “ Dancing With the Stars ” Season 25 on Tuesday night. No one else really had a shot — he triumphed over violinist Lindsey Stirling, the runner - up, and actor Frankie Muniz, the third - place finisher. “ Your skills are just ridiculously out of this world, ” judge Carrie Ann Inaba raved to Fisher after his final performance with his partner, Lindsay Arnold. “ I think you are the most complete male celebrity ever on ‘ Dancing with the Stars, ’ ” Len Goodman added. “ You ’ re right up there with the best we ’ ve seen on this show! ” Bruno Tonioli exclaimed.
